# File Organization (Agent Requested)
- API routes: `src/app/api/<resource>/route.ts`
- Shared types: `src/types/` (one file per domain).
- DB access only inside `src/server/db/` — never import the DB client into components.
- New service: place under `src/services/<name>/`, validate inputs at the boundary,
  return `{ code, message }` style errors (never throw raw strings).
- Utilities: `src/lib/`. Keep them pure and unit-tested.
- Before creating a file, check if a similar one already exists and extend it.
